---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="BeamCash Demo - SkanPay"
  description="See how BeamCash demonstrates the QR checkout workflow SkanPay wants merchants, payment partners, and future financial partners to understand."
  activePath="/beamcash-demo/"
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">BeamCash demo</p>
    <h1>The product demo behind the SkanPay conversation</h1>
    <p>
      BeamCash shows how a seller QR code, buyer checkout screen, and merchant confirmation experience fit together.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section demo-intro">
    <div>
      <img class="beamcash-wordmark" src="/beamcash/beamcash-wordmark.svg" alt="BeamCash" />
      <p class="eyebrow">Why it is here</p>
      <h2>BeamCash demonstrates the experience. SkanPay is the gateway vision.</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">
        Use the demo to see the flow before a deeper merchant, bank, or payment partner conversation.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="spec-panel">
      <div class="spec-row">
        <span>BeamCash</span>
        <p>Working MVP that shows the user experience.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="spec-row">
        <span>SkanPay</span>
        <p>Patent-pending QR payment gateway model and partner opportunity.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="spec-row">
        <span>Boundary</span>
        <p>Demo only. This page does not process live payments.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Walkthrough</p>
        <h2>Follow the checkout path</h2>
      </div>
      <p>
        The demo is intentionally narrow: set up the seller, scan the QR code, review checkout.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="walkthrough">
      <article class="demo-story">
        <div>
          <span>01</span>
          <strong>Seller is ready to accept a QR payment.</strong>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span>02</span>
          <strong>Buyer scans and reviews merchant details.</strong>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span>03</span>
          <strong>The flow gives SkanPay a concrete integration reference.</strong>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="walkthrough-step flow-overview">
        <div>
          <span>Overview</span>
          <h3>Seller setup to checkout review</h3>
          <p>The overview shows the path from seller setup to buyer checkout and post-checkout activity.</p>
        </div>
        <img src="/beamcash/beamcash-product-flow.svg" alt="BeamCash product flow from seller setup to QR sign, buyer checkout, confirmation, and dashboard" />
      </article>
      <article class="walkthrough-step">
        <div>
          <span>Step 1</span>
          <h3>Seller presents the QR code</h3>
          <p>The dashboard gives the seller a visible QR code, readiness state, and recent activity.</p>
        </div>
        <img src="/beamcash/beamcash-seller-dashboard-mobile.png" alt="BeamCash seller dashboard with QR code and readiness status" />
      </article>
      <article class="walkthrough-step">
        <div>
          <span>Step 2</span>
          <h3>Buyer reviews and pays</h3>
          <p>The buyer sees who they are paying, enters an amount, and moves through a familiar checkout screen.</p>
        </div>
        <img src="/beamcash/beamcash-buyer-checkout-mobile.png" alt="BeamCash buyer checkout screen with merchant profile and payment amount" />
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-band">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Next step</p>
      <h2>Use the demo to guide the integration conversation.</h2>
      <p>Share the merchant, wallet, or partner flow you want to evaluate.</p>
    </div>
    <a class="button secondary" href="/contact/">Request a Demo</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
